Demotix Android Form Validator
==============================

This framework allows you to validate inputs of text fields and text views in a convenient way. It is a port of the ustwoâ„¢ iOS Form Validator. It's developed at [Demotix.com](http://www.demotix.com/ "Demotix.com") by Alexandru Badiu.

Features
--------

* Know what went wrong and where
* Create own conditions using regular expressions for example
* Create own validators which contain a collection of conditions